Summary: Toshiba - Reg OM_50 Test steps not clear
Creator: MARUTHAMUTHURAJAN B (DHL IT Services), external
Description:
Test Steps


1. Login to OTM with NAM_INTG_TEST_SYS Role
2. Navigate to Business Process Automation > Integration > Integration Manager
3. Upload the Order Release XML
4. Switch to Planner role
5. Navigate to Order Release > Search the order Release as was seen in the XML
6. Validate the order release is created with all the valid details
7. Switch to Planner role
8. Navigate to Order Release > Search the order Release as was seen in the XML.
9. Select Order Release and click on action Bulk Plan Buy.
10. Click on action Ok.
11. Refresh the page and check whether Shipments are built successfully""
12. Click on the SERVICE PROVIDER Dispatch Contact ID
13.The SERVICE PROVIDER Dispatch Contact page opens up > Edit --> Enter Email address--> Please take a backup for future to revert back.
15. If the SERVICE PROVIDER Dispatch communication method is set as EMAIL then the tender offer will be sent out as an EMAIL notification
16. Close the screen and return back to the Shipment results screen
17. Select the shipment, click on Actions > Secure Resources
18. Scroll to the right and check the status of Secure Resources and the status should be in SECURE RESOURCES_TENDERED
19. Logout from Planner and Login to OTM with NAM_INTG_TEST_SYS Role
20. Go to Transmission manager
21. Under the Transaction Tab provide the shipment ID in the Object field (note: provide the shipment ID with the Domain Name Prefix)
22. Click on the Transmission ID in the Transmission page check the status of the transmission as PROCESSED and element as TenderOffer
23. Upload the modified Order Release XML.
24. Logout from Planner and Login to OTM with NAM_INTG_TEST_SYS Role
25. Go to Transmission manager
26. Under the Transaction Tab provide the shipment ID in the Object field (note: provide the shipment ID with the Domain Name Prefix)
27. Click on the Transmission ID in the Transmission page check the status of the transmission as PROCESSED
28. Open the Transaction XML and check that all the cost details like TotalPlannedCost, TotalActualCost, ShipmentCost are getting reflected as in the updated XML
